Mission Orders

The tuwangis in Babok Hollow are resisting our efforts to explore the mire.

Kill the {@LinkCreature:5#1#tuwangi overseers}, {@LinkCreature:5#2#tuwangi helpers}, and {@LinkCreature:5#3#tuwangi workers}.

Report to Zandra in Lumbertown when mission is complete.
